sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Space
    participant DB as Database

    Note over Client,DB: Owner Registration Flow
    Client->>Space: POST /owner/register<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWE}
    Space->>Space: Extract JWE from header
    Space->>Space: Decrypt JWE with master password
    Space->>Space: Extract JWS from JWE payload
    Space->>Space: Verify JWS signature with public key
    Space->>Space: Parse JWS claims (publicKey, username, iat)
    Space->>DB: Check if user exists by public_key
    DB-->>Space: User not found
    Space->>Space: Generate user ID
    Space->>DB: Create user (id, publicKey, username, role='owner', createdAt)
    DB-->>Space: User created
    Space-->>Client: 201 Created<br/>{message: "Owner registered successfully", user_id}

    Note over Client,DB: User Authentication Flow
    Client->>Space: GET /auth/challenge?username={username}
    Space->>DB: Get user by username
    DB-->>Space: User found
    Space->>Space: Generate random challenge
    Space->>Space: Store challenge with expiration
    Space-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{challenge, expires_at}

    Client->>Space: POST /auth/login<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWS}
    Space->>Space: Extract JWS from header
    Space->>Space: Parse JWS claims (username, challenge, iat)
    Space->>DB: Get user by username
    DB-->>Space: User found with public key
    Space->>Space: Parse user's public key from PEM
    Space->>Space: Verify JWS signature with user's public key
    Space->>Space: Verify challenge matches stored challenge
    Space->>Space: Check challenge expiration
    Space->>Space: Generate JWT token with RSA signing
    Space->>Space: Clean up used challenge
    Space-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{token, expires_at}

    Note over Client,DB: Protected Resource Access
    Client->>Space: GET /protected/resource<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT}
    Space->>Space: Extract JWT from header
    Space->>Space: Verify JWT signature with space public key
    Space->>DB: Get user by ID from JWT claims
    DB-->>Space: User found
    Space-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{protected_data}